### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@username = jankowalski


### ==========================================
### PUBLIC PROFILE (no auth required)
### ==========================================

### Get public profile by username
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/p/{{username}}
Accept: application/json


### ==========================================
### MY PROFILE (locally no token needed)
### ==========================================

### Get my profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me/profile
Accept: application/json

###

### Create profile (first time setup)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/me/profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "jankowalski",
  "displayName": "Jan Kowalski",
  "bio": "Full-stack developer helping startups build products",
  "location": "Warsaw",
  "websiteUrl": "https://jankowalski.dev"
}

###

### Update profile (partial update)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/me/profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bio": "Updated bio: Full-stack developer helping startups build products"
}


### ==========================================
### SERVICES
### ==========================================

### Get my services
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me/services
Accept: application/json

###

### Add service
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/me/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "1h Consultation",
  "description": "We discuss your project, architecture or technical problem",
  "price": 300.00,
  "currency": "PLN",
  "priceLabel": "/ hour"
}

###

### Add second service
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/me/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Code Review",
  "description": "I review your code and provide feedback",
  "price": 500.00,
  "currency": "PLN",
  "priceLabel": "/ project"
}

###

### Delete service (replace with real UUID from GET response)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/me/services/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000


### ==========================================
### LINKS
### ==========================================

### Get my links
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me/links
Accept: application/json

###

### Add link
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/me/links
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "GitHub",
  "url": "https://github.com/jankowalski",
  "iconName": "github"
}

###

### Add second link
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/me/links
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "LinkedIn",
  "url": "https://linkedin.com/in/jankowalski",
  "iconName": "linkedin"
}

###

### Delete link (replace with real UUID from GET response)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/me/links/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000


### ==========================================
### TEST FLOW
### 1. POST /api/me/profile    -> creates user + profile
### 2. POST /api/me/services   -> adds a service
### 3. POST /api/me/links      -> adds a link
### 4. GET  /api/p/jankowalski -> public view (verify everything saved)
### ==========================================
